TOTAL TIME.description: Time used for reading, presolving and solving, excluding copying.

READING TIME.description: Time used for reading of the problem.

COPYING TIME.description: Time used for copying (e.g. from original to master problem).

DETECTION TIME.description: Time used for automatic detection of a problem structure.

PRESOLVING TIME.description: Time used for presolving of the problem.

STATUS.description: Status after solving terminated. 0: unknown, 1: solved (optimal), 2: solved (infeasible), 3: time limit, 4: memory limit, 5: node limit.

ROOT NODE TIME.description: Time spent inside the root node.

DUAL BOUNDS.description: List of development of the dual bounds over time.

HEUR TIME ORIG.description: Time used for heuristics in the original problem.

HEUR CALLS ORIG.description: Number of times heuristics were called in the original problem.

HEUR FOUND ORIG.description: Number of times heuristics found a solution in the original problem.

HEUR TIME MASTER.description: Time used for heuristics in the master problem.

HEUR CALLS MASTER.description: Number of times heuristics were called in the master problem.

HEUR FOUND MASTER.description: Number of times heuristics found a solution in the master problem.

CUTS TIME MASTER.description: Time used for finding/applying cutting planes in the master problem.

CUTS CALLS MASTER.description: Number of times separators were called in the master problem.

CUTS FOUND MASTER.description: Number of times separators found a cutting plane in the master problem.

CUTS APPLIED MASTER.description: Number of times cutting planes were applied in the master problem.

CUTS TIME ORIG.description: Time used for finding/applying cutting planes in the original problem.

CUTS CALLS ORIG.description: Number of times separators were called in the original problem.

CUTS FOUND ORIG.description: Number of times separators found a cutting plane in the original problem.

CUTS APPLIED ORIG.description: Number of times cutting planes were applied in the original problem.

FARKAS TIME.description: Time used for ensuring feasibility of the RMP.

MASTER TIME.description: Total time used for solving the complete master problem.

PRICING TIME.description: Time used for the complete pricing process.

PRICING SOLVER TIME.description: Time used for pricing solvers (e.g. knapsack solver).

PRICING SOLVER TYPE.description: Types of pricing solvers that ran on the problem.

DEGENERACY.description: List of development of the degeneracy over time.

CONS LINEAR.description: Number of linear constraints that could not be classified otherwise.

CONS KNAPSACK.description: Number of constraints that represent a classical knapsack constraint.

CONS LOGICOR.description: Number of constraints that represent a logical 'or'-relation.

CONS SETPPC.description: Number of constraints that represent set-packing, set-partitioning or set-covering constraints.

CONS VARBOUND.description: Number of constraints that represent variable bounds.

LINKING VARS.description: Number of linking variables that connect different blocks.

NBLOCKS.description: Number of blocks (pricing problems) in the decomposition.

NBLOCKSAGGR.description: Number of blocks that were aggregated (at max NBLOCKS).

FIRST SOLUTION TIME.description: Time until first solution was found.

BEST SOLUTION TIME.description: Time until best solution was found.

PD INTEGRAL.description: The average integral (the geometric 'space') between the primal and the dual bound ('avg. gap').

MASTER NCONSS.description: The number of constraints in the master problem.

MASTER NVARS.description: The number of variables in the master problem.

BNB TREE NODES.description: Number of nodes created in the branch-and-bound tree.

BNB TREE LEFT.clearname: Number of BNB Tree Nodes Left
BNB TREE LEFT.description: Number of nodes in the branch-and-bound tree left to be explored after termination.

BNB TREE DEPTH.description: Depth of the created branch-and-bound tree.

BR RULE TIME ORIG.description: Time used for the branching rule 'Original Variable Branching'.

BR RULE TIME GENERIC.description: Time used for the branching rule 'Vanderbeck Generic Branching'.

BR RULE TIME RELPSPROB.description: Time used for the branching rule 'generalized reliability pseudo cost probing branching' (or simply 'pseudo cost branching').

BR RULE TIME RYANFOSTER.description: Time used for the branching rule 'Ryan-Foster Branching'.

BR RULE CALLS ORIG.description: Calls of the branching rule 'Original Variable Branching'.

BR RULE CALLS GENERIC.description: Calls of the branching rule 'Vanderbeck Generic Branching'.

BR RULE CALLS RELPSPROB.description: Calls of the branching rule 'generalized reliability pseudo cost probing branching' (or simply 'pseudo cost branching').

BR RULE CALLS RYANFOSTER.description: Calls of the branching rule 'Ryan-Foster Branching'.

RMP LP CALLS.description: Number of times the restricted master problem was be solved.

RMP LP TIME.description: Time used for solving the restricted master problem.

RMP LP ITERATIONS.description: Total number of iterations all solving runs of the restricted master problem took.

ORIGINAL LP CALLS.description: Number of times the original problem was be solved.

ORIGINAL LP TIME.description: Time used for solving the original problem.

ORIGINAL LP ITERATIONS.description: Total number of iterations all solving runs of the original problem took.

LP FILE.description: Program file (e.g. .lp or .mps) with full path.

DEC FILE.description: Decomposition file (e.g. .dec or .blk) with full path.
